title: LibriVox 7th Anniversary Collection
creator: Various
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of 7th Anniversary Collection by various authors and in various languages To celebrate the 7 years of LibriVox , readers from all around the world have recorded 77 works they have selected, all of which have 7 in their title.We hope you enjoy the amazing mixture they have come up with. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
